ts_data_tbl <- read.csv("Crypto_Hackathon_aRmy.csv")
ts_data_tbl
ts_data_tbl <- ts_data_tbl %>% 
    mutate(
        Date = date %>% mdy_hm(),
        # Day = Date %>% ymd(), 
        Hour_12 = Date %>% hour(), 
        Minute = Date %>% minute()
    ) %>% 
    mutate(
        GainLoss = total - lag(x = total, n = 1), 
        Flag = case_when(
            GainLoss > 0 ~ "Gain", 
            GainLoss == 0 ~ "Neither", 
            GainLoss < 0 ~ "Loss"
        ), 
        Average30Mins = zoo::rollmean(x = total, k = 6, align = "right", fill = NA)
    ) %>% ungroup()
ts_data_tbl
# First six Hours
ts_data_tbl %>%

ts_data_tbl %>% 
    ggplot(mapping = aes(x = Date, y = GainLoss)) +

    #transition_reveal(Date)
ts_data_tbl %>% 
    group_by(Flag) %>% 
    summarise(
        Count = n()
    ) %>% 
    filter(! is.na(Flag)) %>% 
    ungroup() %>% 
    ggplot(mapping = aes(x = Flag, y = Count, fill = Flag)) + 
    geom_col() +
    theme_bw() +
    theme(axis.text.x = element_text(face = "bold", size = 10)) +
    theme(axis.text.y = element_text(face = "bold", size = 10)) +
    transition_states(
    Count,
    transition_length = 2,
    state_length = 2) +
    labs(title = "Crypto Hackathon: Gain vs Losses",
         subtitle = "Team: aRmy",
         x = NULL,
         y = "Total amount",
         caption = "Source: Crypto_Hackathon_aRmy.csv")
